        <obo:IAO_0000114 rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000120"/>
        <obo:IAO_0000115>A clinical tumor stage group according to AJCC 7th edition indicating cancers that are smaller or less deeply invasive without regional disease or nodes.</obo:IAO_0000115>
